<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, October 12 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange
index slipped 12.5 points to close at 2,062.2 Monday.
</P>
<P>
The turnover went up to 9.39 million Kuwaiti dinars (30.98
million U.S. dollars) from Sunday's 6.25 million dinars (20.62
million dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 33.30 million shares changed hands in 760 deals as
against 24.50 million shares in 698 deals the previous day.
</P>
</TEXT>
