<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 13 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on October 14 issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 12 degrees C., max. 18 degrees C., overcast to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 17 degrees C., max. 25 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
