talks with Yugoslav President Slobodan Milosevic with hopes of a
political solution to the Kosovo crisis in sight.
</P>
<P>
When arriving back again in Belgrade, Holbrooke said he saw
"promising possibilities" and was hopeful of a move towards peace.
</P>
<P>
