<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 13 (Xinhua) -- The Sixth China International
Textile Machinery Exhibition (CITME '98) opened today in
Beijing's International Exhibition Center attracting thousands of
participants.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition has attracted 700 major textile machinery
manufacturers from countries and regions throughout the world,
including Germany, Italy, Japan and France.
</P>
<P>
Manufacturers are exhibiting new types of production equipment
for cotton, wool, linen, and silk spinning and weaving, as well as
