and quality control instruments.
</P>
<P>
China's textile industry is undergoing structural readjustments
and the state-owned textile enterprises are phasing out obsolete
spindles as part of an effort to improve production efficiency,
according to a high-ranking official with the China Council for
the Promotion of International Trade (CCPIT).
</P>
