<HEADLINE> Costume Museum Opens in Ningbo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NINGBO, October 13 (Xinhua) -- A new garment museum opened
today in the east China city of Ningbo includes hand-operated
sewing machines and charcoal irons which will bring back memories
to many visitors.
</P>
