<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 0830 GMT, October 13 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK -- U.S. President Bill Clinton said here on Monday
that Yugoslav President Slobodan Milosevic had agreed to end the
seven-month offensive against ethnic Albanians in Serbia's
province of Kosovo and to allow the presence of international
observers.
</P>
<P>
