issued by the Guilin Postal Office on October 14 to mark the Sixth
General Assembly of the Asia-Pacific Parliamentarians Conference
on Environment and Development scheduled for October 14 to 18 in
this tourist city of south China's Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous
Region.
</P>
